<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وأحمد <span class="c2">(١/ ١١٠)</span> وأبو داود <span class="c2">(١٤١٦)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
